_sText:
This is the FINAL version of fy_football, took some time just getting it perfected, but we're up and running now.

This is a fun map where your objective is to score goals by kniving the ball, in the other teams goal of course :p

This has been designed for use on the |SA| server and its 4-a-side football tournamnet.  Sign up your team at www.sourceaddiction.com

Alternativly drop in for a game at the following IP:
194.105.134.64:27015

There are two versions included in the .rar file, one version is the origional and the other is the one that has been edited for the football tournament.

Finally a thank you to the origional creator for making the fy_soccer which was the basis and inspiration fo rthis map and tournament.
